"v.使延期，推迟 【英】 v. 使延期，推迟 ( move to some later time) 【记】 post（在后面）+pone （放）→放在后面→ 推迟 无 【记】post 向后 + pony 小马，向后推马，不是马上(双关)走；post邮政 + pony小马，用马来邮政是延迟 postpone (v.)  c.1500, from Latin postponere ""put after; esteem less; neglect; postpone,"" from post ""after"" (see post-) + ponere ""put, place"" (see position (n.)). Related: Postponed; postponing."
